.TH setRouteBlkDefaultLayer  22.14 "Fri Oct 06 02:12:27 2023" 
.SH Name \fBsetRouteBlkDefaultLayer\fR \-  Specifies the default layers for routing blockages, for both metal layers and cut layers
.SH Syntax \fBsetRouteBlkDefaultLayer\fR   [-help]  {{[-layer <layerName> | {<layerNameList>} | all]   [-cutLayer <layerName> | {<layerNameList>} | all]  [-drcRegionLayer <layerName> | {<layerNameList>} | all]  [-trimMetalLayer <layerName> | {<layerNameList>} | all] } | {-allMetalCut }}
.P Specifies the default layers for routing blockages, for both metal layers and cut layers. The default layers set with this command are applicable for all routing blockages subsequently created using the GUI or the createRouteBlk command. Use this command before creating routing blockages.
.P Note: If any layers are specified with the createRouteBlk command, the layers specified with the setRouteBlkDefaultLayer command are ignored. 
.SH Parameters    "\fB-allMetalCut\fR" Specifies that default routing blockages will be created for all metal layers and all cut layers.  Data_type: bool, required  "\fB-cutLayer <layerName> | {<layerNameList>} | all\fR"  "*" 2 <layerName>: Specifies that default routing blockages will be created for the specified cut layers.  "*" 2 all: Specifies that default routing blockages will be created for all cut layers.  Data_type: list, optional  "\fB-drcRegionLayer  <layerName> | {<layerNameList>} | all\fR"  "*" 2 <layerName>:Specifies that default routing blockages will be created for the specified drc region layers.  "*" 2 all: Specifies that default routing blockages will be created for all drc region layers.  Data_type: list, optional  "\fB-help\fR" Outputs a brief description that includes the type and default information for each setRouteBlkDefaultLayer parameter. For a detailed description of the command and all of its parameters, use the man command:  man setRouteBlkDefaultLayer  "\fB-layer <layerName> | {<layerNameList>} | all\fR"  "*" 2 <layerName>: Specifies that default routing blockages will be created for the specified metal layers.  "*" 2 all: Specifies that default routing blockages will be created for all metal layers.  Data_type: list, optional  "\fB-trimMetalLayer <layerName> | {<layerNameList>} | all\fR"  "*" 2 <layerName>: Specifies that default routing blockages will be created for the specified trim metal layers.  "*" 2 all: Specifies that default routing blockages will be created for all trim metal layers.  Data_type: list, optional 
.SH Example
.P The following command sets default routing blockages for the metal layers1, 2, and 3 and the cut layers 3 and 5.  setRouteBlkDefaultLayer -layer 1 2 3 -cutLayer 3 5 
.SH Related Information
.RS  "*" 2 createRouteBlk  "*" 2 deleteRouteBlk  "*" 2 Floorplanning the Design chapter in the Innovus User Guide
.RE
